title: Falling Off the Aging Cliff at 44
description: Elder millennials have gotten away with seeming young for a long time, but research shows that aging catches up with us at distinct moments — the first comes at 44.
content: Doing karaoke is a great way to feel your exact age, something I only recently remembered. It was two days after Halloween, and my 44th birthday party at Lions Roar Karaoke House in Williamsburg was … [+28240 chars]
